title: BRIEF-Sqli's Wax Interactive designs interactive terminal interface for Leroy Merlin
text:
Oct 26 Sqli SA :
* Leroy Merlin chose Wax Interactive to design the interface for an in-store interactive terminal designed to help customers choose colours for their home Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom:)
